&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;Support the building of robust data models downstream of backend services (mostly in BigQuery) that support internal reporting, machine learning as well as financial and regulatory use cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on optimisation of our Data Warehouse, spotting opportunities to reduce complexity and cost.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define and manage best practices for our Data Warehouse. This may include payload design of source data, logical data modelling, implementation, metadata and testing standards.&lt;/li&gt;
