&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set standards and ways of working with data across Monzo, working collaboratively with others to make it happen.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take established best practices and standards defined by the team, applying them within other areas of the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate and effectively work with colleagues from other disciplines to monitor and improve data quality within the warehouse.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Contribute to prioritisation of data governance issues&lt;/li&gt;
