&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our team⭐&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;347&quot; data-end=&quot;641&quot;&gt;Our Borrowing business is growing rapidly across both existing products and a range of new initiatives. From credit cards and loans to emerging lending products, we’re building solutions that give customers greater control, transparency, and flexibility in how they manage their finances.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;643&quot; data-end=&quot;879&quot;&gt;If you’re interested in using data to understand lending performance, improve decision-making, and support the development of credit strategies, this role offers the opportunity to work on meaningful problems with clear business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;881&quot; data-end=&quot;1118&quot;&gt;This is a high-impact, cross-functional environment where you’ll work closely with Product, Engineering, Data Science, Finance, and Risk &amp;amp; Control to drive sustainable, profitable, and responsible growth across our lending portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
