&lt;p&gt;Our main tech hub is in London, but our data teams are based all over the UK — from Brighton to the Western Isles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We love meeting in person, but there’s no pressure to come into the office, even if you’re nearby. You’ll do your best work where you feel most comfortable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We value flexibility, connection, and wellbeing. You’ll have the freedom to work in a way that fits your life, whether that’s school drop-offs, avoiding rush hour, or making time for what matters most.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work the way that works for you at Monzo! 💼&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🤩 We’d love to hear from you if…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in unsecured lending, ideally within credit cards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong understanding of credit card economics (APR, utilisation, interchange, revolving behaviour, cost of funds, losses)

