&lt;p&gt;It’s an exciting space to disrupt with new technology. Today, many small businesses are underserved by clunky banking tools, expensive finance software, or manual processes that don’t reflect how modern teams actually work. We think Monzo can change that by building simple, powerful collaboration tools for the businesses that need them most.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll set the vision, craft a customer-obsessed strategy, and create the execution engine that turns ambition into reality. We’re looking for someone who pairs exceptional product taste with strong analytical depth, thrives in ambiguity, and can inspire teams to deliver world-class outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
